comment: /**  * Register a message handler.  * @return {@code true} if the handler was subscribed or {@code false} if it  * was already subscribed.  */
code: /**  * Register a message handler.  * @return {@code true} if the handler was subscribed or {@code false} if it  * was already subscribed.  */ boolean subscribe(MessageHandler handler).

comment: /**  * Un-register a message handler.  * @return {@code true} if the handler was un-registered, or {@code false}  * if was not registered.  */
code: /**  * Un-register a message handler.  * @return {@code true} if the handler was un-registered, or {@code false}  * if was not registered.  */ boolean unsubscribe(MessageHandler handler).
